        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName><hi rend="print">Down, | Beckenham, Kent.</hi></placeName>
                    <date>June 2<hi rend="superscript">nd</hi></date>
                    <salute>Dear Sir</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>I am much obliged to you for sending me the fact about the Dog, which I am glad to hear, &amp; it corroborates previous statements which I have heard.—<ref target="#foot.f2"/></p>
<p>Dear Sir | Yours faithfully | Ch. Darwin</p> 
                </div>
